iaik.pdf.asn1objects

Class SpDocSpecification

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
      • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.SpDocSpecification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iaik.asn1.ASN1Type

    public class SpDocSpecification
extends SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
    This class represents the signature policy qualifier of type SpDocSpecification. The value of this signature policy qualifier is either a IA5String or an ObjectID, indicating the URI to or the OID of the signature policy's technical specification.
